details.text: Does the Examinee look older than age stated?
Any disease/disorder of Central or Peripheral nervous system, history/evidence of aneurysm,hydrocephalus etc.?
Any disease / disorder of renal or reproductive system like nephritis. hydronephrosis. prostate enlargement, hydrocele etc.?
Any disease / disorder of Endocrine system or any autoimmune disease like thyroid disorder, Crohn's disease SLE etc.?
Is the examinee currently pregnant? If yes. how many weeks?
Has the examinee ever suffered / suffering from Gestational diabetes, preeclampsia or any other pregnancy related complications?
Are you a Healthcare professional (Includes Doctors, Nurses, Pathologist, Paramedics, Pharmacist, Ward helpers, Individuals working in Hospitals/Clinics having a COVID-19 Ward)?
